ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: No, I would not.There is too much students' presentations.
I would only recommend the course to other students if the class was smaller such that less class time would be invested in student presentations.
Not unless the proportion of lectures increases.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I learned some frontier of the research in this course.
I wish I could have learned more with additional lectures by Prof Vytlacil. It is a very useful subject matter for my educational goals.
The class forced me to think seriously about the applied econometrics paper.
